      "title": "Compute the discriminant",
      "content": "For $$x^2 - 12x + 27 = 0$$, identify $$a = 1$$, $$b = -12$$, $$c = 27$$.<br/>Compute the discriminant: $$b^2 - 4ac = (-12)^2 - 4(1)(27) = 144 - 108 = 36$$.",
